OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales has said he needs
OL,7,Fto be in a "calm state" to watch
OL,8,FHamnet as he attended the Bafta
OL,9,Fawards, adding: "I'm not at the
OL,10,Fmoment".
OL,12,FWilliam, who is president of the arts
OL,13,Fcharity, walked down the red carpet
OL,14,Fwith his wife, the Princess of Wales,
OL,15,Fat the Royal Festival Hall by the
OL,16,FSouth Bank in London on Sunday.
OL,18,FThe event marked their first public
OL,19,Fappearance since Andrew's arrest.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@WO]qD@QOUrD@GO]
