OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,FAndrew was arrested on Thursday on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice, spending 11 hours in custody
OL,9,Fon his 66th birthday, after
OL,10,Fallegations he shared sensitive
OL,11,Finformation with Jeffrey Epstein
OL,12,Fduring his time as the UK's trade
OL,13,Fenvoy.
OL,15,FSpeaking to Elaine Bedell, chief
OL,16,Fexecutive of the Southbank Centre, and
OL,17,FAllison Kirkby, chief executive of BT
OL,18,FGroup, The Prince of Wales said that
OL,19,Fhe had not yet watched Hamnet, which
OL,20,Fwon Outstanding British Film.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
