OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771872516
OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,F"I need to be in quite a calm state
OL,7,Fand I'm not at the moment," he said.
OL,8,F"I will save it."
OL,10,FHamnet, the big-screen adaptation of
OL,11,FMaggie O'Farrell's award-winning
OL,12,Fnovel, tells the story of the family
OL,13,Flife of William Shakespeare and the
OL,14,Fdeath of his young son.
OL,16,FThe film was nominated for 11 Baftas,
OL,17,Fwith Jessie Buckley winning Best
OL,18,Factress in a leading role for her
OL,19,Fstarring role.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@[O]pD@AOUpD@QO]
