OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,FChatting with the chairwoman of
OL,7,FBafta's film committee, Emily
OL,8,FStillman, and executive director of
OL,9,Fthe charity's awards and content, Emma
OL,10,FBaehr, the princess said: "Yes, I
OL,11,Fthink it was a very bad idea
OL,12,Factually... ended up with very puffy
OL,13,Feyes."
OL,15,FShe said it was "really very very
OL,16,Fpowerful", praising the "fantastic"
OL,17,Fand "raw" music score and talking
OL,18,Fabout its portrayal of
OL,19,F"intergenerational grief".
