OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,FTowards the end of the show, William
OL,7,Fpresented the Bafta fellowship award
OL,8,Fto NBCUniversal's chair of
OL,9,Fentertainment, Dame Donna Langley, for
OL,10,Fher outstanding contribution to film
OL,11,Fand television.
OL,13,FHe said: "Her transformative
OL,14,Fleadership and unwavering commitment
OL,15,Fto creative partnership have brought
OL,16,Fsome of this century's most iconic
OL,17,Ffilms to the big screen and to
OL,18,Faudiences around the world.
