OL,3,CPrince William says he is 'not in a
OL,4,Ccalm state' as he attends Bafta Awards
OL,6,F"She has championed films that have
OL,7,Fshaped culture, and is responsible for
OL,8,Fsome of our most beloved franchises."
OL,10,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,11,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,12,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,13,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
